<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <body>
        <header>
            <%- include ('header/header.ejs') %>
        </header>
        <main>
            <!-- ======= 문의 하기 Section ======= -->
            <section id="faq">
                <div class="container">
        
                <div class="section-title" style="margin-top: 130px;">
                    <h2>문의 하기</h2>
                    <p>에이스텍에 대해 문의할 내용을 아래 양식에 적어주세요.</p>
                </div>
        
                 <!-- ======= 문의 하기 form ======= -->      
                    <form id="contact-form" style="margin-top: 50px;">
                      <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="col-lg-6 form-group">
                          <input type="hidden" name="contact_number">
                          <input type="text" class="form-control" name="to_name" placeholder="성함"/>
                          <div class="validate"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6 form-group">
                          <input type="email" class="form-control" name="to_email" placeholder="Email 주소"/>
                          <div class="validate"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="subject"placeholder="제목"/>
                        <div class="validate"></div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="form-group">
                        <textarea class="form-control" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="문의 내용"></textarea>
                        <div class="validate"></div>
                      </div>
                      <div style="text-align: center;">
                        <div class="contact2" style="margin-top: 50px;"><button type="submit" style="outline:none" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#intro">전송 하기</button></div> 
                      </div>                    
                    </form>   
        </main>
        <div class="modal fade" id="intro" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="introHeader" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
            <div class="modal-dialog">
                <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header">
                        <h4 class="modal-title">에이스텍</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">                        
                        <p>관리자에게 이메일이 전송 되었습니다!</p>
                        <p>확인 이후 해당 이메일로 답장 드리겠습니다.</p>                    
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">닫기</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <footer>
            <%- include ('footer/footer.ejs') %>
        </footer>
    </body>
</html>


